<title>HTML forms</title>
</head>
<body>
  <iframe src="html5.png" scrolling="no" align="right" 
  width="200px" height="200px" name="frame" frameborder="0">
    <p>OOPs Ur browser iframe not supporting.....................!!</p>
  </iframe>
</body>
</html>

Example:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
